name: NFT FREAKS TRIBUTE (for fun)
description:
[sound on]

Tribute to one of the realest heads in the game!

Thank for the wisdom encouragement and life experience you share with theNFT space on a daily basis.

We appreciate you and the way you can boost up other creators and set people on path to real organic growth and success in this field, not just by what they create -- but by how they act and treat others in this space.

You are a solid dude and an excellent example to learn from.

BUT -- you issued a challenge today and I just had to respond! Ha ha ha ha!  Hope you appreciate the humor.

Maybe the collector is out there for this rare gem!

111 Tezos is just pennies in ETHERIUM, right?
Maybe the right "whale" is out there to scoop this 1/1.

Ha ha ha -- peace and best of luck you all you creators out there! 

Anyway hope it makes some folks smile!

Sincerely,

HP LoveBux
